pective.\n\nThis is session 66. The ONLY work done was fixing state corruption #50 (stories 16-5/6/7/8 reverted to `review` by Ralph's stale state). All 74 stories are done. Sprint is complete. Ralph keeps running no-op sessions.\n\nProduce a retrospective that covers:\n1. **Session summary** — no-op session, state corruption fix only\n2. **Issues analysis** — the recurring state corruption (50th time), Ralph not stopping\n3. **Cost analysis** — from the cost report, focus on waste from no-op sessions\n4. **What went well** — sprint is complete (74/74 stories, 17/17 epics)\n5. **What went wrong** — 50+ no-op sessions wasting tokens\n6. **Lessons learned** — Ralph needs a sprint-complete exit condition\n7. **Action items** — stop Ralph, fix stale-state overwrite bug\n\nWrite the retrospective to _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-28.md. If it already exists, append to it with a `---` separator and timestamp.\n\nDo NOT ask the user any questions — proceed autonomously.\nDo NOT run git commit. Do NOT run git add. Do NOT modify sprint-status.yaml.","agentId":"adbcfef3f905e7019","agentType":"general-purpose","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Retrospective appended to `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-28.md`.\n\nSummary of findings:\n\n- **Session 66**: No-op. State corruption fix #50 (same 4 stories: 16-5/6/7/8). Sprint remains complete at 74/74 stories.\n- **Total cost**: $749.65 across 5,486 API calls. Estimated waste from ~50 no-op sessions: $300-400 (40-53%).\n- **Cost since last retro (session 60)**: +$11.30, all wasted.\n- **Root cause unchanged**: Ralph overwrites on-disk `done` state with stale in-memory `review` state. No sprint-complete exit condition exists.\n- **Action required**: Stop Ralph. Fix the stale-state overwrite bug. Add sprint-complete exit condition. Make `done` a terminal state."}],"totalDurationMs":63833,"totalTokens":29177,"totalToolUseCount":8,"usage":{